                  <text>the trustees of Te Rūnanga o Ngāti Manawa providing the Crown with—</text>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">i</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a registrable covenant in relation to section 7 SO 431616 in the form set out Part 11 of the schedule of the deed of settlement (the <emphasis style="bold">Kāramuramu covenant</emphasis>); and</text>
                    </para>
                  </label-para>
                  <label-para skeleton="no">
                    <label auto.number="no" denominator="yes">ii</label>
                    <para>
                      <text>a registrable right of way easement in gross in favour of the Minister of Conservation over the area marked <quote.in quote="1">B</quote.in> on SO 431616 in the form set out Part 12 of the schedule of the deed of settlement.</text>
                    </para>
